      "id": 200,
      "options": {
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:18px 22px;\">\n  <h1 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600; color:#e5e7eb; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Who's using SupportBot \u2014 and who's a problem?</h1>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0; color:#a3a3a3; font-size:14px; max-width:980px; line-height:1.55;\">\n    ACME's internal SupportBot routes every employee chat through <code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:3px; color:#fbbf24;\">sb-router</code> (intent classifier) to one of nine specialists (<code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:3px; color:#fbbf24;\">sb-hr-info</code>, <code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:3px; color:#fbbf24;\">sb-it-troubleshoot</code>, <code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:3px; color:#fbbf24;\">sb-policy-finder</code>, \u2026). AI is usage-priced, so a handful of heavy users or abusers can swing the monthly bill 10\u00d7 while the average employee is a rounding error. <b style=\"color:#e5e7eb;\">This view ranks internal SupportBot users by combined offender score</b> (cost percentile \u00d7 50 + waste % \u00d7 0.5) and shows which agents they're hitting.\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr); gap:14px; font-size:13px; color:#d4d4d4; line-height:1.5;\">\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">\u2460 Leaderboard</span> \u2014 calls, tokens, 24h cost, projected 30d, waste %, quality, problem score. Sorted by problem score.</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">\u2461 Per-user agent mix</span> \u2014 stacked tokens by sb-* specialist. Outliers in one agent often indicate misuse.</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">\u2462 Time trends</span> \u2014 cost/hour and calls/min. Spikes outside business hours = paste-bombs, injection probes, or exfil attempts.</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">\u2463 Quality (preview)</span> \u2014 fleet and bottom-10 LLM-judge scores. Populates once the Sigil quality.business_value_score evaluator is firing.</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:12px; font-size:12px; color:#737373;\">Tip: pick a single user from the <b>User</b> dropdown to scope the whole dashboard. Scope is hard-pinned to <code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:3px; color:#a3a3a3;\">ai_o11y_specialist=~\"sb-.*\"</code> so only SupportBot traffic counts.</div>\n</div>",
        "mode": "html"
      },
      "title": "",
      "transparent": false,
      "type": "text"
    },
